







#lg A	sa-gida


@(1-5=c41308.A.A.1) Righteous lord who determines destiny! Born to @wDN{Ninlil}, @wDN{Suen}, beloved son of @wDN{Ninlil}, @wDN{Suen}, having no rival in the @wTN{E-kur}, the house of @wDN{Enlil}: your divine powers are majestic divine powers granted by @wDN{An}!

@(6-12=c41308.A.A.6) Your father, holy @wDN{An}, has bestowed upon you divine powers to which other gods cannot aspire. @wDN{Enlil} has decreed them to you in destiny. The lord of the holy lustration rites, @wDN{An}, has established them. ……, sacred lion of the gods, justly honoured, you are the light of heaven.
$ (1 line fragmentary)
