#lg C	jicgijal


@(7-9=c41308.B.C.7) O shrine @wSN{Urim}! Within, through their intricate craftsmanship, the @wDN{Enki} and @wDN{Ninki} deities have perfected the divine powers with their righteousness, and the @wDN{Anuna} gods stand there in service.

